"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我们需要挺过萨卡兹驻军的反扑，只要公爵们开始与萨卡兹交火，我们就可以抓住机会。","id":153,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"......计划会顺利进行的。","id":155,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯......我只是稍稍有些不安。","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这里有一些......让我感到压抑的东西。我不知道那是什么。","id":159,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#10$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"一开始，我以为只是诺伯特区的气氛太过沉重，后来，我以为是......特蕾西娅小姐想要再度向我展现什么。","id":161,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"可似乎都不是。","id":163,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"......阿米娅，我在本舰的时候，曾听见有些萨卡兹称呼你为“魔王”。","id":165,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"对于你来说，这意味着什么？你明明不是一名萨卡兹。","id":167,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"你会希望自己是一个能带领属民的统治者吗？还是个冲锋在前的英雄？","id":168,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":169},{"type":"charslot","id":170},{"type":"Text","text":"推进之王轻抚着身边的诸王之息，这把剑仍然冰冷，一如往常。","id":171},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......我不知道，推进之王小姐，我必须坦诚。","id":173,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"特蕾西娅小姐为我们所有人描绘了那么一个未来......我仍然坚信，她所诉说的那个未来才是值得生活的。","id":175,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"可是，她把这顶冠冕交给了我，却没有告诉我到底应该如何抵达那里。如今，她甚至......站在了我们的对面。","id":177,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我只能尝试说服自己，这是她对我的考验。","id":179,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......我其实没有想好怎么面对她。她会对我说什么？她会怎么看待我做的事情？","id":181,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我为自己选择的道路......会让她失望吗？","id":185,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我不知道自己是不是一个......值得被交付“魔王”权柄的人。","id":187,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"可你仍然选择承担这份职责。","id":189,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我同样在担忧，自己无法成为那个人们期冀中的人。","id":191,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"那个能够劈开天灾的英雄，那个能够团结人民的君主......","id":192,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我要怎么才能做到？我要怎么才能回应那些......如此沉重的期待？","id":193,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","tex